   Originality/value - Research evaluating the impact of PBL on students' knowledge in Lean and Six Sigma courses does not currently exist. Statistical analysis of survey responses from both the Lean and Six Sigma courses was performed using a x(2) test of independence to examine how similar the students received knowledge from the use of the semester project.
