ctive learning methods. Also, the paper reviews challenges and constraints that we faced while trying to teach this course. The analysis results show the effectiveness of our approach. Also, our students have expressed a high level of satisfaction, and in a survey, they indicated that the skills they learned in the course are highly applicable to their careers, facilitating their interviews for the engagement within IT companies.
